ComicInfo.Title: The Swordsman; Cracked Interviews the Trekker King; The Billy Pluckett Story; College for Panhandlers; Famous Animal Celebrities; Cracked Predictions for the 1980's; Cracked Handbook for Restaurant Owners; The Coming Mini-Auto Age; Star Drek the Moving Picture
ComicInfo.Summary:
A swashbuckling hero kills the wicked king but accidentally kills the good queen when he celebrates.
Nanny interviews the world's greatest Star Trek fan.
Celebrities from the animal kingdom who are quite similar to human celebrities.
The crew of the Enterprising investigate the mysterious vessel Voyge as it hurls toward Earth. After solving the problem they decide their next voyage should be back to television where people liked them.
